previewPlan.name: New Year Resolution 3 week 3wk habit
previewPlan.description:
Your 2022 resolution starts now. This plan will help you develop the habits you need to succeed in 2022. 

If you think of the tortoise and the hare we are setting you up to be the tortoise. Going out of the gates hot might seem like a good plan, but consistency and easing into things will always ensure long term success. 

Start your best year yet by spending the next 3 weeks making training a consistent part of your daily routine.
